== Overview == It is located in the southwestern part of [[:en:Mishima, Shizuoka|Mishima City]], at the northern end of the Nagabuse district, on the east bank of the Sakai River, adjacent (to the south) to the Matsumoto district's {{ill|Takahashi Shrine (Mishima City)|ja|高橋神社 (三島市)|lt=Takahashi Shrine|lt_ja=高橋神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takahashi Shrine (Mishima City)|qq=}}.
